  <body>

    <a href="#main">Skip to content</a>

    <header class="[ o-wrapper ] [ site-header ]">

      <div class="site-header__brand">
        <h1 class="site-name"><span>Cardiff</span> Delivers</h1>
        <p class="site-strapline">Local delivery information for Cardiff's food and drink businesses, during the <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/coronavirus-covid-19/">Coronavirus (COVID-19)</a> closures.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="[ site-nav ] [ o-flow ]">

        <!-- FUNDRAISER -->
        <div class="[ notification ] [ o-flow ]">
          <p>Support this amazing fundraiser:</p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/feeding-nhs-staff-at-uhw-heath-hospital" rel="external">
              Feed NHS staff at UHW
              <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M19 6.41L8.7 16.71a1 1 0 1 1-1.4-1.42L17.58 5H14a1 1 0 0 1 0-2h6a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v6a1 1 0 0 1-2 0V6.41zM17 14a1 1 0 0 1 2 0v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V7c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h5a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5v12h12v-5z"/></svg>
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- MAIN NAV -->
        <nav>
          <ul class="[ site-nav__list ] [ o-flow ]">
            <li><a href="#vendor">Get your business on this list</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">About this list</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>

      </div>

    </header>

    <main id="main">
      <div class="o-wrapper">
        {% block content %}
        {{ content | safe }}
        {% endblock %} 
      </div><!-- .o-wrapper -->
    </main>

    <aside class="[ o-wrapper ] [ o-flow ]">
      <h2 id="vendor">Get your business on this list</h2>
      <p>It would be great to support as many local businesses as we can through this challenging time. To be added to the list, email Matthew &mdash; <a href="mailto:hello@matthewpassmore.co.uk">hello@matthewpassmore.co.uk</a> &mdash; with details of what you offer, where you deliver to, how people can order, and how best to make contact.</p>
      <h2 id="about">About this list</h2>
      <p>Thank you to <a href="https://twitter.com/ViningSarah">Sarah Vining</a> and <a href="https://wearecardiff.co.uk/2020/03/27/you-can-support-cardiffs-independent-businesses-during-covid-19-coronavirus-shutdown/">We Are Cardiff</a> for their hard work collating information to get things moving. You can view <i>We Are Cardiff</i>'s <a href="https://wearecardiff.co.uk/2020/03/27/you-can-support-cardiffs-independent-businesses-during-covid-19-coronavirus-shutdown/">blog post of listings</a>, or <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1e7-a8KZ0Hg5PSihXrTV-LAjZdANwvqh2">download Sarah's lovely printable versions</a>.</p>
      <p>This is a project by <a href="https://matthewpassmore.co.uk">Matthew Passmore</a>, runs on <a href="https://11ty.dev/">Eleventy</a> and is hosted by <a href="https://netlify.com/">Netlify</a>. </p>
    </aside>

    <footer class="o-wrapper">
      <p class="demands"><strong>Stay at home. Wash your hands.</strong></p>
    </footer>

    <script>{% include 'js/main.js' %}</script>
